    "biomes": ["forest"],
    "weight": 7,
    "one_shot": false,
    "text": "Fresh bone fragments pressed into the earth around the path, in a pattern. Claw scrapes on the bark at shoulder height—not the scrapes of a natural animal sharpening its claws, but deliberate marks. Something left these as a message.",
